```

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ“Œ 5. Context Sharing in Multi-Agent Systems

In multi-agent systems:

* Agent A performs research
* Agent B writes report
* Agent C verifies output

ğŸ‘‰ MCP ensures:

* All agents access shared memory
* Consistent context
* No duplication

