ğŸ§© 6. Example Scenario

 Goal:

Generate monthly performance report.

Flow:

1. Planner agent sets tasks
2. Research agent retrieves past data
3. Data agent analyzes numbers
4. Writer agent drafts report
5. Reviewer agent checks quality

All agents access **shared memory via MCP**.

