----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

ğŸ“Œ 9. MCP vs Direct Memory Access

| Feature             | Direct Access | MCP-Based Memory |
| ------------------- | ------------- | ---------------- |
| Structure           | Manual        | Standardized     |
| Security            | Weak          | Strong           |
| Scalability         | Low           | High             |
| Multi-Agent Support | Limited       | Excellent        |

